Prime Minister Jose Luis Rodriguez
Zapatero named Interior Minister Alfredo Perez Rubalcaba as
first deputy prime minister and government spokesman and
Trinidad Jimenez as foreign minister. He spoke at a news
conference in Madrid today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
